data.description:
MOTIVATED!Welcome to your dream home nestled on 19.6 acres of picturesque countryside! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern elegance.  The heart of the home showcases the open concept living, kitchen, and dining areas, allowing for effortless flow and connection. The kitchen is a masterpiece, featuring exquisite knotty alder cabinetry, stainless-steel appliances, and wood-look tile that adds warmth and durability.  Custom framing around windows and doors enhances the home's unique personality, while allowing ample natural light to flood in, illuminating the space with a comforting ambiance.
     The Primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and en suite bath with large walk-in shower. 3 additional bedrooms and a hall bath that provides a double vanity shower/tub combo and beautiful storage cabinets for all the things. Additional features of this exceptional property include a 2-car garage, ensuring your vehicles are sheltered from the elements, an above-ground pool where you can relax and soak in the sunshine, and a guest house with a 1/2 bath and one bedroom. 
  The property is graced with a 30x30 barn that is a hobbyist's delight. Complete with a propane heater, a water system that's heat traced to prevent freezing, and concrete floors, this barn is a versatile space suitable for various activities. The white barn, equipped with water and primed for electrical setup, offers four exterior roll-up doors and two interior roll-up doors. Its spacious layout lends itself to ample storage, and the barn's past as a stall area means converting it back for equestrian use would be a breeze. The perimeter of the property is fenced with a combination of pipe fencing and barbed wire, ensuring security and privacy for you and your livestock.  This property sets just 1.2 miles from Arbuckle Lake and offers plenty of room for guests and recreational parking.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable home yours!
